data.description:
Available for quick close! Existing VA loan is assumable at 2.75%.
Welcome to your dream home in Elk River! This meticulously upgraded residence on a premium lot caters to discerning buyers seeking comfort and sophistication. The kitchen boasts a large center island, smart double ovens, upgraded quartz countertops, and a convenient pot filler. The primary ensuite is a haven of luxury with a double vanity, a Jacuzzi soaking tub with heated bubbles, and a spacious walk-in closet.

The garage is a Minnesota marvel, fully insulated and heated, featuring a separately metered circuit for electric vehicles. This sanctuary ensures comfort even in the coldest winters. Beyond, numerous enhancements make this gem a must-see. Come, and experience Elk River living at its finest—where modern amenities meet timeless elegance. Your dream home awaits!
